{
  "title": "ENFERMEDADES DE CÉLULAS FALCIFORMES Y OTRAS HEMOGLOBINOPATÍAS",
  "guid": "4F6557F73F0C5F8A58C7FDD1",
  "filepath": "/sessions/bold-jolly-cerf/mnt/Dropbox/- Esquemas/- Entidades clínicas/Cardiología/Williams. ENFERMEDADES DE CÉLULAS FALCIFORMES Y OTRAS HEMOGLOBINOPATÍAS-2025-1.smmx",
  "root": {
    "id": "0",
    "parent": "-1",
    "text": "ENFERMEDADES DE CÉLULAS FALCIFORMES\nY OTRAS HEMOGLOBINOPATÍAS",
    "guid": "cHAqOgMRZmMMpCM9IGNNGQ",
    "children": [
      {
        "id": "1",
        "parent": "0",
        "text": "## DEFINICIONES",
        "guid": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "2",
            "parent": "1",
            "text": "- Hemoglobinopatías: sustituciones de nucleótido único en cadenas α, β, γ o δ",
            "guid": "PNi4_16qfm8j9D1rTyaMxw",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "3",
            "parent": "1",
            "text": "- Variantes de Hb: designadas con letras o lugares donde se encontraron",
            "guid": "BCyO20OdQtQaKtSTe--A7Q",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "4",
            "parent": "1",
            "text": "- Trastorno de células falciformes: estados donde ocurre adopción de forma falciforme durante desoxigenación",
            "guid": "QRN1iGIEzccyof7tFQmQrg",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "5",
            "parent": "1",
            "text": "- Enfermedades de células falciformes (ECF): causan morbilidad (HbSS, HbSC, HbS-β-talasemia, HbSD)",
            "guid": "eK-riC8SgEp1yOk8JVeiYA",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "6",
        "parent": "0",
        "text": "## ETIOLOGÍA Y\nPATOGENIA",
        "guid": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "7",
            "parent": "6",
            "text": "- Polimerización de\nhemoglobina",
            "guid": "",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "8",
                "parent": "7",
                "text": "- Mutación HbS: sustitución ácido glutámico → valina en posición 6 de cadena β",
                "guid": "fnfYQjTVSMZ-H6AxbugCfA",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "9",
                "parent": "7",
                "text": "- Moléculas desoxiHbS forman polímeros → eritrocitos menos deformables y adherentes",
                "guid": "N-avKQrDw24PS0-VRVLZaA",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "10",
                "parent": "7",
                "text": "- Ciclos repetidos → células falciformes irreversibles → aumento viscosidad y estasis vascular",
                "guid": "C7CdkBV3pZ8V2xn3YloyUQ",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "11",
            "parent": "6",
            "text": "- Factores que influyen en\nadopción de forma falciforme",
            "guid": "",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "12",
                "parent": "11",
                "text": "- Concentración intracelular de Hb (MCHC)",
                "guid": "YkMVAW6CH-MYtrF6HxvOAA",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "13",
                "parent": "11",
                "text": "- Presencia de otras Hb (HbF protectora)",
                "guid": "TSyeUjyq7uVuQlrIUVktLQ",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "14",
                "parent": "11",
                "text": "- Tensión de oxígeno, pH, temperatura",
                "guid": "AEgxuQhtL1tNSK4bQVunQg",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "15",
            "parent": "6",
            "text": "- Otras vías\npatogénicas",
            "guid": "QR_9RRQYDHx_Z36NI2MSRg",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "16",
                "parent": "15",
                "text": "- Óxido nítrico: hemólisis libera Hb → captación NO → disfunción endotelial",
                "guid": "anH9I3_qrQhWZTfwYyGoqw",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "17",
                "parent": "15",
                "text": "- Activación inflamatoria: mediadores proinflamatorios → adhesión → vasooclusión",
                "guid": "Lv0tU0wuISwIeUsLLXUFlQ",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "18",
                "parent": "15",
                "text": "- Coagulación activada, isquemia-reperfusión, alteración homeostasis catiónica",
                "guid": "AQNp8waY6z0cXQgROOoZHA",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "19",
                "parent": "15",
                "text": "- Señalización anormal por adenosina",
                "guid": "EVyuqyuoV6Z-PPKEHQ1MOw",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "20",
        "parent": "0",
        "text": "##\nMANIFESTACIONES\nCLÍNICAS",
        "guid": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "21",
            "parent": "20",
            "text": "- Crisis",
            "guid": "",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "22",
                "parent": "21",
                "text": "- Vasooclusivas/dolorosas: más comunes, frecuencia variable, dolor por hipoxia e infarto",
                "guid": "AposXxgeMAdCfuBGT8bKsQ",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "23",
                "parent": "21",
                "text": "- Aplásicas: supresión eritropoyesis (parvovirus B19, deficiencia folato)",
                "guid": "VMke7TDBOw4hH_feVRFQpg",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "24",
                "parent": "21",
                "text": "- Secuestro esplénico: acumulación masiva de eritrocitos en bazo",
                "guid": "OS5qam5opfkWbPfoI6BnjQ",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "25",
                "parent": "21",
                "text": "- Hiperhemolíticas: hemólisis aumentada",
                "guid": "blNTAmzSL9kGwhA4HVCAVQ",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "26",
            "parent": "20",
            "text": "- Sistema\ncardiopulmonar",
            "guid": "BULTFUOlv_V3TfUsB9z_dA",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "27",
                "parent": "26",
                "text": "- Síndrome tórax agudo: fiebre, leucocitosis, infiltrado nuevo (principal causa de mortalidad)",
                "guid": "OQBRBQ87W0RKxYXqOgO6-A",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "28",
                "parent": "26",
                "text": "- Hipertensión pulmonar crónica: riesgo aumentado de mortalidad",
                "guid": "FdRGgWcijfty7dQVJzD1LA",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "29",
                "parent": "26",
                "text": "- Taquicardia, soplos cardiacos",
                "guid": "EsrloXEqxplEPkFoU-ri5g",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "30",
            "parent": "20",
            "text": "- Sistema\nnervioso central",
            "guid": "ao4QgXjDwgQFnl-QI7x66w",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "31",
                "parent": "30",
                "text": "- Apoplejías trombóticas: mayor riesgo en niños, recurrentes",
                "guid": "W8Pv_DnM1XJXo8olMI0O6Q",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "32",
                "parent": "30",
                "text": "- Velocidad alta en Doppler transcraneal: predictor de riesgo",
                "guid": "Zyxn_RwLV3hHXOJ4VX-6_w",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "33",
                "parent": "30",
                "text": "- Infartos cerebrales silenciosos, declinación neurocognitiva",
                "guid": "CN2HUU4e8rBy0DtUQd3YVw",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "34",
            "parent": "20",
            "text": "- Sistema\ngenitourinario",
            "guid": "XVpN9D2VwT574ZNPcy6UdQ",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "35",
                "parent": "34",
                "text": "- Hipostenuria, necrosis papilar, hematuria",
                "guid": "JLhPOW7PZ2QaX4miN4M02g",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "36",
                "parent": "34",
                "text": "- Microalbuminuria, proteinuria, enfermedad renal crónica",
                "guid": "X_ot_l6dywoLbhfAZT0BEw",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "37",
                "parent": "34",
                "text": "- Priapismo, enuresis nocturna",
                "guid": "IkOK_wK8DOxtGgCIfgd6-w",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "38",
            "parent": "20",
            "text": "- Sistema\nmusculoesquelético",
            "guid": "",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "39",
                "parent": "38",
                "text": "- Retraso crecimiento y pubertad",
                "guid": "PIjiX0S9yq0ulInlJxby4A",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "40",
                "parent": "38",
                "text": "- Infartos óseos, dactilitis, necrosis avascular",
                "guid": "PYGMsTQy6XVK023LJK30rw",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "41",
            "parent": "20",
            "text": "- Otras\nmanifestaciones",
            "guid": "UD5A7RIwUEN6La-uWRvIPw",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "42",
                "parent": "41",
                "text": "- Bazo: esplenomegalia → autoesplenectomía (HbSS)",
                "guid": "YE9C82z96wMa-aCWPamQ6A",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "43",
                "parent": "41",
                "text": "- Hígado: disfunción, cálculos biliares",
                "guid": "KpOsQRbbM-Uw2CVdT0v7ew",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "44",
                "parent": "41",
                "text": "- Ojo: retinopatía proliferativa",
                "guid": "BaqbSks3rv8GzzBVZaTJSA",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "45",
                "parent": "41",
                "text": "- Úlceras en piernas",
                "guid": "",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "46",
                "parent": "41",
                "text": "- Embarazo: riesgo aumentado para madre y feto",
                "guid": "KdV6CRI9SBZK4cpbTBkFCA",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "47",
        "parent": "0",
        "text": "## DATOS DE\nLABORATORIO",
        "guid": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "48",
            "parent": "47",
            "text": "- Anemia: Hb 50-110 g/L en HbSS, normocrómica/normocítica",
            "guid": "FPlVAjf7yuNKIIAEUYI3YQ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "49",
            "parent": "47",
            "text": "- Células falciformes y en diana en frotis, reticulocitosis",
            "guid": "fLmVkXi1Cel4mSpBOjsiQg",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "50",
            "parent": "47",
            "text": "- Leucocitosis, trombocitosis (médula reactiva y asplenia)",
            "guid": "LOfzXkNsmAxe6RbxfSY0Sw",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "51",
            "parent": "47",
            "text": "- Electroforesis: detecta HbS, HbA2 y HbF aumentadas",
            "guid": "VZzoT1kWxqBWQfyKNewrQw",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "52",
        "parent": "0",
        "text": "## TRATAMIENTO",
        "guid": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "53",
            "parent": "52",
            "text": "- Medidas\ninespecíficas",
            "guid": "RhSxo3E7nSBzlbwrcKhd5A",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "54",
                "parent": "53",
                "text": "- Ácido fólico, vacunación antineumocócica",
                "guid": "CBbRBiRt4Yg_9FlfDcFsUA",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "55",
                "parent": "53",
                "text": "- Profilaxis con penicilina hasta 5 años",
                "guid": "b6WQiEbDibVzZjWYGXsKkQ",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "56",
            "parent": "52",
            "text": "- Medidas\nespecíficas",
            "guid": "WQDRyz5H__NllA-abfomzQ",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "57",
                "parent": "56",
                "text": "- Hidroxiurea: 15-35 mg/kg/día, reduce crisis, aumenta HbF",
                "guid": "dkPK1y-0j54_fF4vcv1gaA",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "58",
                "parent": "56",
                "text": "- Trasplante de células madre: curativo en pacientes seleccionados",
                "guid": "KGmZhzgViHAtOIKqVVGM5Q",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "59",
                "parent": "56",
                "text": "- Terapia génica: experimental, promisoria",
                "guid": "e4IgfQwhmZxSd8EwUR8IzA",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "60",
                "parent": "56",
                "text": "- Transfusión: aumenta Hb, disminuye proporción células falciformes",
                "guid": "ZThgPCi5vbsHCzQPK00R3w",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "61",
                "parent": "56",
                "text": "- Nuevos fármacos: L-glutamina, crizanlizumab",
                "guid": "GfVa23qg8Dob9W_DIgwr4Q",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "62",
            "parent": "52",
            "text": "- Manejo de\ncomplicaciones",
            "guid": "",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "63",
                "parent": "62",
                "text": "- Crisis vasooclusivas: hidratación, analgesia, temperatura adecuada",
                "guid": "Hw7Rw1vpySMvzZgxDrRiSw",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "64",
                "parent": "62",
                "text": "- Síndrome tórax agudo: transfusiones, antibióticos, broncodilatadores",
                "guid": "Iq1S2CMzzckoL2zce64kow",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "65",
                "parent": "62",
                "text": "- Accidentes cerebrovasculares: programa transfusión crónica",
                "guid": "YXvNvQ3DfHZpqEtwV7-YlA",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "66",
                "parent": "62",
                "text": "- Priapismo: hidratación, transfusión, epinefrina intracavernosa",
                "guid": "PXgMFCkkqZ9KvPj8ZeGlmw",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "67",
                "parent": "62",
                "text": "- Sobrecarga hierro: quelantes (deferasirox, desferrioxamina)",
                "guid": "YToyEHf1e6Y7MzKAXLxSjQ",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "68",
        "parent": "0",
        "text": "## OTRAS\nHEMOGLOBINOPATÍAS",
        "guid": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "69",
            "parent": "68",
            "text": "- Hemoglobina C\n(HbC)",
            "guid": "BBcVQg2q87Et21tZaU91fg",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "70",
                "parent": "69",
                "text": "- Sustitución ácido glutámico → lisina en posición 6 cadena β",
                "guid": "NmSxbDTmj2kUnIddUFoMRw",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "71",
                "parent": "69",
                "text": "- Estado homocigótico: anemia hemolítica leve, esplenomegalia",
                "guid": "L4d_ozCR9yFyZjgpTpZRZg",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "72",
            "parent": "68",
            "text": "- Hemoglobina D\n(HbD)",
            "guid": "PaQsz0lf_XE2l060Ht5e3w",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "73",
                "parent": "72",
                "text": "- Migra como HbS en electroforesis, solubilidad normal",
                "guid": "DHvARCIz0FpdSrOxLykTHA",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "74",
                "parent": "72",
                "text": "- Estados heterocigoto y homocigoto: asintomáticos",
                "guid": "RWeeJAV6II4q1ze_JuNr4Q",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "75",
            "parent": "68",
            "text": "- Hemoglobina E\n(HbE)",
            "guid": "QVV5F3HKgTV7mrFsRWyOWg",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "76",
                "parent": "75",
                "text": "- Común en sudeste asiático",
                "guid": "Ez2dBBR_gy9-owR1ULWpGQ",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "77",
                "parent": "75",
                "text": "- Rasgo: asintomático con microcitosis leve",
                "guid": "f3V05il2DMUuvAPYNdomUg",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "78",
                "parent": "75",
                "text": "- Con β-talasemia: anemia y esplenomegalia moderadas",
                "guid": "XlycLkNYizYGNDKZDeQb0g",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
